# FASTNETPAY SSTP router accounts.
# Format:
# username  server  password  stable-router-vpn-ip
#
# Keep the live file at /etc/ppp/chap-secrets with mode 600.
# Use scripts/production/add-sstp-router.sh to add real router accounts.
# The SSTP installer maps the fourth column to the active PPP session so
# FASTNETPAY can always manage the router by this stable 10.100.x.x IP.
#
# fastnet-rb951-001  *  CHANGE_LONG_RANDOM_PASSWORD  10.100.1.1
